	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yes u have alot of money for a wiz at your lvl. A good quest to do once u hit 24 is gem inland gauntlets quest. Once u have ports u get the gauntlets in about 30min they r good for casters and r worth up to 125pp.<br>Kiting is snaring/rooting a monster and nuking it while it is helpless. U get a snare at lvl 29 and u already have root.<br>Yes there is a spell that does that at higher lvls it is called harvest.<br>Azartz Sunscars lvl 30 wizzy of UCoV<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
