<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=9959186551841></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9959186551841><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=11&mid=9959186551841>RE: What is kite?</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=11&mid=9959186551841#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=46723><span id=Scholar>gdnom</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>59 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Jul 23rd 4:04 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.24]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Expect to be poor.  Expect to be poor until 26.<br><br>Don't worry about money.  200pp is alot prior to Level 20.  Worry about just being able to buy all your spells.<br><br>There is not much for items for wizards to improve your killing ability, just your spells.  When I was under 20, I funded most of my spells thru fishing and killing same level mobs.<br><br>Once you can teleport, the money will start flowing.  I am currently level 40 and have close to 5k pp in my bank.  About 4k of that came from teleports. 1k from loots.  Before level 40, I only had 500pp.<br><br>But if your goal is to make money and not level.  If you have 200pp with you right now.  Go to East Commons.  This works best if you have 2 computers.  Find out what people are selling then lookup the prices in the internet.  Offer less than the going rate.  Then sell it for the going rate so you'll make a profit.  Keep on doing this until you get the amount of money you want.. &lt;grin&gt;  Good luck.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
